rComments: I could tell it was her first time teaching. Material is not accessible, and she isnt the most helpful prof. I wouldnt take her again in the future. Her class is long, boring, and she doesnt post slides with enough info online.

She's a new professor, very sweet and nice. It was a 3-hour class and it's a very jammed pack 3 hours. She doesn't record the class and doesn't post all her slides so you need to be there to take notes. Had to write an op-ed, then write a response to a classmate's op-ed, had to create a grant proposal. Midterm + final open book, MCQ and long answer
